longBusinessSummary: Hammer Fiber Optics Holdings Corp., a telecommunications company, engages in investing in wireless technology. The company develops high speed fixed wireless service for residential, small business, and enterprise clients using its wireless fiber platform, Hammer Wireless AIR, as well as mobility networks, such as 4G/LTE; and over-the-top services comprising voice, SMS, and collaboration. It is also involved in the provision of hosting services, including cloud and colocation. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Point Pleasant Beach, New Jersey.
